meta {
  name: Logout
  type: http
  seq: 5
}

post {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
  body: none
  auth: none
}

docs {
  No server-side session to revoke (ADR-0064, stateless bearer token) — this
  always returns 204. Logging out for real just means discarding {{token}}
  client-side; clear the environment's token var yourself if you want to
  simulate that here.
}
